title: Sax Sulphite Drawing Paper, 50 lb, 9 x 12 Inches, Extra-White, Pack of 500 - 053925
description: High quality, 100% sulphite paper is standard weight and accepts dry media in addition to wet media including tempera, watercolor and brushed-applied ink. Standard weight paper has exceptional body and strength, has perfect texture for all dry media renderings, and erases well. The brilliant white stock enhances colored pencil, heavy black pencil and charcoal drawings.
